H0.text: People born on the 1st March have which sign of the Zodiac. Aquarius

H1.text: People born on the 1st March have which sign of the Zodiac. Aries

H2.text: People born on the 1st March have which sign of the Zodiac. Taurus

H3.text: People born on the 1st March have which sign of the Zodiac. Picese

A4.text: The vernal equinox, which defines the start of Aries, currently occurs near the end of the constellation Pisces.

A5.text: The vernal equinox occurs annually around 21 March, which marks the beginning of the zodiac sign Aries.
